title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 150] Minimal, Neofolk, Synth
description:
Here are the records some of you guys and gals have requested recently. They are rare, of course not if you have turntable and $$ to buy them online. Not Only Bones is a re-issue of the original album, again issued on vinyl. Others are rips from the original records. Please seed as long as you can. Keep this archive of rare and obscure 80's music alive.

Courage Of Lassie - The Temptation To Exist [1986]

Iko - Iko [1983]

Max & Malcolm - Max & Malcolm [1982]

Not Only Bones - Not Only Bones [1984]
